{"tid":1239454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要！！] 620 死線","createTime":"2019-06-18T07:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T07:40:22.000Z","uid":247187,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e7023e25afc29683fa4357fd75445088fd9de80b","tid":1239454,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:26:02.000Z","msg":"我要求6月20 下午3點前林鄭做齊以下四樣！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回逃犯條例</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無條件釋放所有被捕人士</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收回暴動定性</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">追究黑警過度使用武力</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">否則我地就衝擊並包圍立法會！！</span></span><br />\n重申多次 揀20號係因為21號有明日大嶼嘅會要開 唔好俾佢地混淆視聽！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揀3點係因為5點搞一陣就入夜 對勇武派嚟講好危險！！<br />\n仲可以等人放工嚟接力<br />\n辛苦晒文宣巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要廣傳係件好易同好快嘅事 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係一個合適嘅時間就要同大家夾過</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">大家謹記<br />\n不分化、不篤灰、不抹黑、不割𥱊！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有咩唔啱就傾到啱 唔好玩分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6eb3ebfb517525a45a11f3b07a625c1e4b9eb28d","tid":1239454,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eafdf6d6a501b2a883723510d6128a814021c1a6","tid":1239454,"uid":247187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T07:26:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"